urdu transliteration text:
tehro ke mai atharween mannat to berha doonphir leke balaayein tujhe jeene ki dua doonsadqay ho ye maadar haay haay ali akbar
Oh Ali Akbar! Oh Ali Akbar!
@HujjatELC

itna to zara tehro tumhein dulha banaloonbas ek jhalak sehre ki sughra ko dhikaloonbechain thi qaahar haay haay ali akbar
Oh Ali Akbar! Oh Ali Akbar!
@HujjatELC

atthara baras paal ke parwaan chadayawo gaysuwon wala hai mera khoon may nahaayaye kya hua dilbar haay haay ali akbar
Oh Ali Akbar! Oh Ali Akbar!
@HujjatELC

aaye jo hamay lootne qaimay may sitamgarmaa degi sadaayein ali akbar ali akbarchin jaayegi chaadar haay haay ali akbar
Oh Ali Akbar! Oh Ali Akbar!
@HujjatELC
